---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cannabis Data Exchange Standard">
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cdes-green-700 to-cdes-green-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Cannabis Data Exchange Standard</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-cdes-green-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          An open standard for interoperable cannabis data. Share strains, COAs, terpene profiles, and lab results across systems.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/getting-started" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-cdes-green-700 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-cdes-green-50 transition">Get Started</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Acidni-LLC/cdes-spec" class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-cdes-green-700 transition">View on GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Why CDES?</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-cdes-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cdes-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Standardized Schemas</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">JSON Schema definitions for strains, COAs, terpene profiles, and cannabinoid data.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-cdes-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cdes-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Reference Data Library</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Official terpene library with CAS numbers, effects, and scientific references.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-cdes-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cdes-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Ready-to-Use SDKs</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Python SDK for validation and data transformation. TypeScript SDKs coming soon.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Simple to Use</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 overflow-x-auto">
        <pre class="text-sm text-green-400"><code>pip install cdes

from cdes import validate_strain

result = validate_strain(strain_data)
print(result.valid)  # True</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ready to adopt CDES?</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Join the growing community using CDES for cannabis data interoperability.</p>
    <a href="/getting-started" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-cdes-green-600 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-cdes-green-700 transition">Start Integrating Today</a>
  </div>
</Layout>
